CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, September 13, 1952, pg. 27 reads: "Golfdom's Best - Being average wasn't good enough at the South Park golf course last week as the above champions proved in annexing UGA crowns...Next is Alice Stewart of Detroit, new Women's Amateur champ...Teenie Harris Photos."
TitMainTitle: Portrait of Alice Stewart wearing light colored baseball cap and light colored shirt with dark trim, putting golf ball on South Park golf course for UGA champions
